37. A container, comprising:
an external housing including a sidewall extending between a first end and a second end and surrounding an internal chamber, said internal chamber being closed at said second end by a support surface;
a porous surface positioned in said internal chamber and extending from said support surface;
a storage chamber partially defined by said porous surface; and
a first desiccant positioned between said sidewall and said porous surface.
